This repository is the source code for both the iPhone and Android versions of the MTGJudge app, and any resource files and update scripts associated with them.  The app is available for free on both App Stores at http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mtgjudge/id363484335 and https://market.android.com/details?id=com.mtgjudge, respecitvely.  

If you are interested in helping this project in any capacity, I would be glad to accept your help!  Just send me an email at numegil@gmail.com and we'll see what you can do :)



